'''奥斯卡·菲格罗亚'''（{{bd|1983年|4月27日||}}），出生于[[薩拉戈薩_(安蒂奧基亞省)|薩拉戈薩]]，哥伦比亚举重运动员<ref>{{cite web|script-title=es:OSCAR ALBEYRO FIGUEROA MOSQUERA|publisher=Comité Olímpico Colombiano|url=http://www.coc.org.co/sitio/images/stories/hojas/pesas/lvp-hv-ofigueroa.pdf|accessdate=2016-08-09|archive-date=2020-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200121111701/http://www.coc.org.co/sitio/images/stories/hojas/pesas/lvp-hv-ofigueroa.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，曾参加过四届奥运。在2012年伦敦奥运会上，菲格罗亚实现突破，获得举重62公斤级银牌<ref>{{Cite web|title = Weightlifting at the 2012 London Summer Games: Men's Featherweight|url = http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2012/WLT/mens-featherweight.html|website = Olympics at Sports-Reference.com|accessdate = 2015-06-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200418132348/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/summer/2012/WLT/mens-featherweight.html|archive-date = 2020-04-18|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。在2016年里约奥运会上，他又获得了同一项目的金牌，並於賽後宣布退役。<ref>{{cite news|title=举重名将四战奥运夺冠 现场脱鞋痛哭宣布退役|url=http://2016.qq.com/a/20160809/035037.htm|publisher=腾讯|date=2016-08-09|accessdate=2016-08-09|archive-date=2021-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111014345/https://2016.qq.com/a/20160809/035037.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

